{"tid":1502124,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"港鐵違反左法庭禁制令?","createTime":"2019-08-24T14:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T15:35:10.000Z","uid":145841,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa3d0e72c40fa07878213533935485434432d7d","tid":1502124,"uid":145841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"香港鐵路有限公司已於2019年8月23日取得法庭臨時禁制令（「該命令」），<span style=\"color: red;\">禁止任何人</span>非法地及<span style=\"color: red;\">有意圖地故意阻礙</span>或干擾根據香港鐵路條例（第556章）所定義的<span style=\"color: red;\">鐵路（「該鐵路」）的正常使用</span>、損壞該鐵路任何車站的財物、及於該鐵路任何車站造成騷擾。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/interim-injunction-order.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fmain%2Finterim-injunction-order.html&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84om5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=c0612d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/interim-injunction-order.html</a>"},{"pid":"05bf58c4091d5c683fb461366fe3fbb7e7192591","tid":1502124,"uid":145841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0314732f24d63040a06e55d7266dc92a9eb964","tid":1502124,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7c24d53bce2a2e522f2e248e44156b0ac3b0ab5","tid":1502124,"uid":12179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:57:27.000Z","msg":"有意圖地:為左運黑警"},{"pid":"31d3bda4962f107571ce4d626b5f9059d9aa405a","tid":1502124,"uid":145841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94987af35125b829c35689fa158039279ae53683","tid":1502124,"uid":153311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"偽造文書同藐視法庭<br />\n港鐵揀樣認咗佢"},{"pid":"3e757269c9be6ff775